_aChangeLog.text: Added automatical shortcut open for the defenders, if noone passes the kz part in 110-120 seconds on town, drain and wind sections
Increased HP of the final door from 850 to 1170

_sText:
Map is made for NiDE 2023 Mapping Contest. And got 1st place in it.

Map info

The map is based on the game Jump King.

Legend has it there is a smoking hot babe at the top!

This is unusual map, that contains both ze and kz gameplay. If you played Jump King game, you know what to wait from that. You'll need to jump a lot and fall aswell. And once you obtain the jumping power, you get that hot babe on the tower. 

Map features

  • Main babe level with two modes - beginner and godlike jumper (first one is for the team game and the second for hardcore jumpers)
  • Crows quest (follow the nasty crow until you or the crow get defeated)
  • Hot smoking babe on the top (she is really hot)
  • Lots of various and mythical human items
  • Fall down oriented map structure
  • Lots of secret and unexpected ways to reach the top
  • Lots of jumps that surely will break you down
  • Some references to other popular games and films
  • Hidden lore, that can be solved by character dialogs and the environment

Jump king plus plugin

Plugin incudes speedrun timer, automatic update of new records and the database with all the server records being saved.
Players, who get into server top 4 and keep the place on this top, will obtain the unique skin on this map on the server.
Players, who beat the whole godlike jumper mode, will get forever the crown and the trail on the map.
For getting the plugin for your server, pm me (Headsh#6641) or HaRyDe (HaRyDe#0054) in discord.
